(29,1757685715,2,'BE',1,0,33,'tt_content','{\"oldRecord\":{\"pi_flexform\":\"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\" standalone=\\\"yes\\\" ?>\\n<T3FlexForms>\\n    <data>\\n        <sheet index=\\\"sDEF\\\">\\n            <language index=\\\"lDEF\\\">\\n                <field index=\\\"title\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">PROJECTS\\/WORK EXPERIENCE<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"portfolio\\\">\\n                    <el index=\\\"el\\\">\\n                        <field index=\\\"61bb49681bb88771005091\\\">\\n                            <value index=\\\"container\\\">\\n                                <el>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">t3:\\/\\/file?uid=27<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"description\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">I have 6 years TYPO3 experience working in a small TYPO3 agency as an integrator\\/developer.<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"headline\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">TYPO3<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                <\\/el>\\n                            <\\/value>\\n                            <value index=\\\"_TOGGLE\\\">1<\\/value>\\n                        <\\/field>\\n                        <field index=\\\"61bb4a540ec52352802764\\\">\\n                            <value index=\\\"container\\\">\\n                                <el>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">t3:\\/\\/file?uid=32<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"description\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">I worked as a software developer\\/ 3rd line support in London between 1996 and 2009. I worked for a bank, a large American consultancy, document management system companies and local government. <\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"headline\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">Programmer<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                <\\/el>\\n                            <\\/value>\\n                            <value index=\\\"_TOGGLE\\\">1<\\/value>\\n                        <\\/field>\\n                        <field index=\\\"61bb4a59df85e090340053\\\">\\n                            <value index=\\\"container\\\">\\n                                <el>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">t3:\\/\\/file?uid=33<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"description\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">I was on the winning team in the M\\u00fcnster Hackathon 2024. We used the open data api to produce weekly podcasts summarizing local government decisions in a bitesize format.<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"headline\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">Hackathon<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                <\\/el>\\n                            <\\/value>\\n                            <value index=\\\"_TOGGLE\\\">1<\\/value>\\n                        <\\/field>\\n                        <field index=\\\"61bb4a632e9f3046467276\\\">\\n                            <value index=\\\"container\\\">\\n                                <el>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">t3:\\/\\/file?uid=31<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"description\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">I recently completed a short course as a Digital Shaper with Techlabs M\\u00fcnster. My team used python to analyse statistics on weather and bicycle use patterns in M\\u00fcnster.<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"headline\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">Data science<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                <\\/el>\\n                            <\\/value>\\n                            <value index=\\\"_TOGGLE\\\">1<\\/value>\\n                        <\\/field>\\n                    <\\/el>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">12<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"description\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">Showcase your baking skills to the whole world through well-documented recipes, baking videos or presentations, and firmly established connections. If you are a master baker and have a knack for advertising your skills to the world, you will create out of yourself a fine freelance baker.<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n            <\\/language>\\n        <\\/sheet>\\n    <\\/data>\\n<\\/T3FlexForms>\"},\"newRecord\":{\"pi_flexform\":\"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\" standalone=\\\"yes\\\" ?>\\n<T3FlexForms>\\n    <data>\\n        <sheet index=\\\"sDEF\\\">\\n            <language index=\\\"lDEF\\\">\\n                <field index=\\\"title\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">PROJECTS<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"portfolio\\\">\\n                    <el index=\\\"el\\\">\\n                        <field index=\\\"61bb49681bb88771005091\\\">\\n                            <value index=\\\"container\\\">\\n                                <el>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">t3:\\/\\/file?uid=27<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"description\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">I have 6 years TYPO3 experience working in a small TYPO3 agency as an integrator\\/developer.<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"headline\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">TYPO3<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                <\\/el>\\n                            <\\/value>\\n                            <value index=\\\"_TOGGLE\\\">1<\\/value>\\n                        <\\/field>\\n                        <field index=\\\"61bb4a540ec52352802764\\\">\\n                            <value index=\\\"container\\\">\\n                                <el>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">t3:\\/\\/file?uid=32<\\/value>\\n                                    <\\/field>\\n                                    <field index=\\\"description\\\">\\n                                        <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">I worked as a software developer\\/ 3rd line support in London between 1996 and 2009. I worked for a bank, a large American consultancy, document