(54,1757764531,2,'BE',1,0,35,'tt_content','{\"oldRecord\":{\"pi_flexform\":\"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\" standalone=\\\"yes\\\" ?>\\n<T3FlexForms>\\n    <data>\\n        <sheet index=\\\"sDEF\\\">\\n            <language index=\\\"lDEF\\\">\\n                <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">0<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"headline\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">Sarah McCarthy<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"text\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">I am a web programmer living in M\\u00fcnster, Germany. I create web sites for clients, mainly in TYPO3 but I also work with Wordpress. I have an interest in new technologies, including AI.<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n            <\\/language>\\n        <\\/sheet>\\n    <\\/data>\\n<\\/T3FlexForms>\"},\"newRecord\":{\"pi_flexform\":\"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\" standalone=\\\"yes\\\" ?>\\n<T3FlexForms>\\n    <data>\\n        <sheet index=\\\"sDEF\\\">\\n            <language index=\\\"lDEF\\\">\\n                <field index=\\\"image\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">1<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"headline\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">Sarah McCarthy<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"text\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">Ich bin ein Webprogrammierer und lebe in M\\u00fcnster, Deutschland. Ich erstelle Websites f\\u00fcr Kunden, haupts\\u00e4chlich in TYPO3, arbeite aber auch mit Wordpress. Ich interessiere mich f\\u00fcr neue Technologien, einschlie\\u00dflich KI.<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n            <\\/language>\\n        <\\/sheet>\\n    <\\/data>\\n<\\/T3FlexForms>\"}}',0,'0400$1b6a81c0b01bbc91e39ea354b0aebf5a:d31fbabb978b029b9ff62ab107e0a