(57,1757764570,1,'BE',1,0,36,'tt_content','{\"CType\":\"ns_portfolio\",\"categories\":\"0\",\"layout\":\"0\",\"frame_class\":\"default\",\"space_before_class\":\"large\",\"space_after_class\":\"\",\"colPos\":\"0\",\"date\":0,\"header_layout\":\"0\",\"header_position\":\"\",\"imagewidth\":0,\"imageheight\":0,\"imageorient\":\"0\",\"imagecols\":\"2\",\"recursive\":\"0\",\"list_type\":\"\",\"sectionIndex\":1,\"hidden\":0,\"starttime\":0,\"endtime\":0,\"l18n_parent\":\"33\",\"l18n_diffsource\":\"{\\\"CType\\\":\\\"ns_portfolio\\\",\\\"assets\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"bodytext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"bullets_type\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"categories\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"category_field\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"colPos\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"cols\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"editlock\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"endtime\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"fe_group\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"file_collections\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"filelink_size\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"filelink_sorting\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"filelink_sorting_direction\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"frame_class\\\":\\\"default\\\",\\\"header\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"header_layout\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"header_link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"header_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"hidden\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"image\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"image_zoom\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"imageborder\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"imagecols\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"imageheight\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"imageorient\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"imagewidth\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"l10n_source\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"layout\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"linkToTop\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"list_type\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"media\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"pages\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pi_flexform\\\":\\\"<?xml version=\\\\\\\"1.0\\\\\\\" encoding=\\\\\\\"utf-8\\\\\\\" standalone=\\\\\\\"yes\\\\\\\" ?>\\\\n<T3FlexForms>\\\\n    <data>\\\\n        <sheet index=\\\\\\\"sDEF\\\\\\\">\\\\n            <language index=\\\\\\\"lDEF\\\\\\\">\\\\n                <field index=\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\">\\\\n                    <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">PROJECTS<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                <field index=\\\\\\\"portfolio\\\\\\\">\\\\n                    <el index=\\\\\\\"el\\\\\\\">\\\\n                        <field index=\\\\\\\"61bb49681bb88771005091\\\\\\\">\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"container\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                <el>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">t3:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/file?uid=27<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">I have 7 years TYPO3 experience working in a small TYPO3 agency as an integrator\\\\\\/developer. I am the co-team lead of the TYPO3 Documentation Team and contribute regularly to the official documentation. I am a member of the Education Team and help create official certification questions.<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"headline\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">TYPO3<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                <\\\\\\/el>\\\\n                            <\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"_TOGGLE\\\\\\\">1<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                        <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                        <field index=\\\\\\\"61bb4a540ec52352802764\\\\\\\">\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"container\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                <el>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">t3:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/file?uid=32<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">I worked as a software developer\\\\\\/ 3rd line support in London between 1996 and 2009. I worked for a bank, a large American consultancy, document management system companies and local government. <\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"headline\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">Programmer<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                <\\\\\\/el>\\\\n                            <\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"_TOGGLE\\\\\\\">1<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                        <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                        <field index=\\\\\\\"61bb4a59df85e090340053\\\\\\\">\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"container\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                <el>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">t3:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/file?uid=33<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">I was on the winning team in the M\\\\u00fcnster Hackathon 2024. We used the M\\\\u00fcnster Open Data API (Oparl Open Data interface) to produce weekly podcasts summarizing local government decisions in a a bitesize format.<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"headline\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">Hackathon<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                <\\\\\\/el>\\\\n                            <\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"_TOGGLE\\\\\\\">1<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                        <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                        <field index=\\\\\\\"61bb4a632e9f3046467276\\\\\\\">\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"container\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                <el>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">t3:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/file?uid=31<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">I recently completed a short course as a Digital Shaper with Techlabs M\\\\u00fcnster. My team used python to analyse statistics on weather and bicycle use patterns in M\\\\u00fcnster.<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                    <field index=\\\\\\\"headline\\\\\\\">\\\\n                                        <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">Data science<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                                    <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                                <\\\\\\/el>\\\\n                            <\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                            <value index=\\\\\\\"_TOGGLE\\\\\\\">1<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                        <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                    <\\\\\\/el>\\\\n                <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                <field index=\\\\\\\"image\\\\\\\">\\\\n                    <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">12<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n                <field index=\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\">\\\\n                    <value index=\\\\\\\"vDEF\\\\\\\">Showcase your baking skills to the whole world through well-documented recipes, baking videos or presentations, and firmly established connections. If you are a master baker and have a knack for advertising your skills to the world, you will create out of yourself a fine freelance baker.<\\\\\\/value>\\\\n                <\\\\\\/field>\\\\n            <\\\\\\/language>\\\\n        <\\\\\\/sheet>\\\\n    <\\\\\\/data>\\\\n<\\\\\\/T3FlexForms>\\\",\\\"records\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"recursive\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"rowDescription\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"sectionIndex\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"selected_categories\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"space_after_class\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"space_before_class\\\":\\\"large\\\",\\\"starttime\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"subheader\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"table_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"table_class\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"table_delimiter\\\":\\\"124\\\",\\\"table_enclosure\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"table_header_position\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"table_tfoot\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"tx_impexp_origuid\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"uploads_description\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"uploads_type\\\":\\\"0\\\"}\",\"bullets_type\":\"0\",\"cols\":\"0\",\"table_class\":\"\",\"table_delimiter\":\"124\",\"table_enclosure\":\"0\",\"table_header_position\":\"0\",\"table_tfoot\":0,\"target\":\"\",\"uploads_description\":0,\"uploads_type\":\"0\",\"pid\":15,\"sorting\":512,\"fe_group\":\"\",\"rowDescription\":\"\",\"editlock\":0,\"sys_language_uid\":1,\"l10n_source\":33,\"l10n_state\":\"\",\"table_caption\":\"\",\"tx_impexp_origuid\":1,\"header\":\"\",\"header_link\":\"\",\"subheader\":\"\",\"bodytext\":\"\",\"imageborder\":0,\"image_zoom\":0,\"pages\":\"\",\"records\":\"\",\"linkToTop\":0,\"pi_flexform\":\"<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\" standalone=\\\"yes\\\" ?>\\n<T3FlexForms>\\n    <data>\\n        <sheet index=\\\"sDEF\\\">\\n            <language index=\\\"lDEF\\\">\\n                <field index=\\\"title\\\">\\n                    <value index=\\\"vDEF\\\">PROJECTS<\\/value>\\n                <\\/field>\\n                <field index=\\\"portfolio\\\">\\n                    <el index=\\\"el\\\">\\n                        <field index=\\\"61bb49681bb88771005091\\\"