(43,25,1757953313,1757952322,1,0,0,0,'',256,'',0,0,0,0,NULL,'{\"CType\":\"\",\"bodytext\":\"\",\"categories\":\"\",\"colPos\":\"\",\"date\":\"\",\"editlock\":\"\",\"endtime\":\"\",\"fe_group\":\"\",\"frame_class\":\"\",\"header\":\"\",\"header_layout\":\"\",\"header_link\":\"\",\"header_position\":\"\",\"hidden\":\"\",\"layout\":\"\",\"linkToTop\":\"\",\"rowDescription\":\"\",\"sectionIndex\":\"\",\"space_after_class\":\"\",\"space_before_class\":\"\",\"starttime\":\"\",\"subheader\":\"\"}',0,0,0,0,'default',2,NULL,0,'text',0,0,'','',0,'',0,'','','','<h2><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Effective Date: 15.9.25</p>\r\n<p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>1. No Cookies</strong></h3>\r\n<p>We respect your privacy and have chosen <strong>not to use cookies</strong> or any similar tracking technologies on this website. We do not collect any browsing data or track your activity across the web.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>2. Information We Collect</strong></h3>\r\n<p>The only personal information we collect is what you <strong>voluntarily provide</strong> when you use our contact form. This may include:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Your name</li><li>Your email address</li><li>Any other information you include in your message</li></ul>\r\n<p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect any personal data unless you choose to share it with us.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>3. How We Use Your Information</strong></h3>\r\n<p>We only use the information you submit through the contact form to:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Respond to your inquiry</li><li>Provide customer support</li><li>Follow up on your request (if needed)</li></ul>\r\n<p>We do <strong>not</strong> use your information for marketing purposes, nor do we share it with third parties unless required by law.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>4. Data Storage and Security</strong></h3>\r\n<p>We take reasonable steps to protect the information you provide. Your data is stored securely and only accessible to authorized personnel. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>5. Data Retention</strong></h3>\r\n<p>We retain your contact form submissions only as long as necessary to respond to your request or fulfill our legal obligations. You may request that we delete your information at any time (see Section 6).</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>6. Your Rights</strong></h3>\r\n<p>You have the right to:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you</li><li>Request correction or deletion of your information</li><li>Withdraw your consent at any time</li></ul>\r\n<p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at: [Insert Email Address]</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>7. Third-Party Links</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Our website may contain links to other websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their privacy policies separately.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>8. Changes to This Policy</strong></h3>\r\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><strong>9. Contact Us</strong></h3>\r\n<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your information is handled, please contact us at:</p>\r\n<p><strong>sarahmccarthy.de</strong><br />sarahmccarthy123@yahoo.com<br />&nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,NULL,0,'',0,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,'',0,0,'',124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','','',0,0),
(44,25,1757953313,1757952422,1,0,0,0,'',512,'',0,1,43,43,NULL,'{\"CType\":\"text\",\"assets\":\"0\",\"bodytext\":\"<h2><strong>Privacy Policy<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Effective Date: 15.9.25<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>1. No Cookies<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>We respect your privacy and have chosen <strong>not to use cookies<\\/strong> or any similar tracking technologies on this website. We do not collect any browsing data or track your activity across the web.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>2. Information We Collect<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>The only personal information we collect is what you <strong>voluntarily provide<\\/strong> when you use our contact form. This may include:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>Your name<\\/li><li>Your email address<\\/li><li>Any other information you include in your message<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>We do <strong>not<\\/strong> collect any personal data unless you choose to share it with us.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>3. How We Use Your Information<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>We only use the information you submit through the contact form to:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>Respond to your inquiry<\\/li><li>Provide customer support<\\/li><li>Follow up on your request (if needed)<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>We do <strong>not<\\/strong> use your information for marketing purposes, nor do we share it with third parties unless required by law.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>4. Data Storage and Security<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>We take reasonable steps to protect the information you provide. Your data is stored securely and only accessible to authorized personnel. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>5. Data Retention<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>We retain your contact form submissions only as long as necessary to respond to your request or fulfill our legal obligations. You may request that we delete your information at any time (see Section 6).<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>6. Your Rights<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>You have the right to:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you<\\/li><li>Request correction or deletion of your information<\\/li><li>Withdraw your consent at any time<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at: [Insert Email Address]<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>7. Third-Party Links<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Our website may contain links to other websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their privacy policies separately.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>8. Changes to This Policy<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<h3><strong>9. Contact Us<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your information is handled, please contact us at:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>sarahmccarthy.de<\\/strong><br \\/>sarahmccarthy123@yahoo.com<br \\/>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"bullets_type\":\"0\",\"categories\":\"0\",\"category_field\":\"\",\"colPos\":\"2\",\"cols\":\"0\",\"date\":\"0\",\"editlock\":\"0\",\"endtime\":\"0\",\"fe_group\":\"\",\"file_collections\":\"\",\"filelink_size\":\"0\",\"filelink_sorting\":\"\",\"filelink_sorting_direction\":\"\",\"frame_class\":\"default\",\"header\":\"\",\"header_layout\":\"0\",\"header_link\":\"\",\"header_position\":\"\",\"hidden\":\"0\",\"image\":\"0\",\"image_zoom\":\"0\",\"imageborder\":\"0\",\"imagecols\":\"2\",\"imageheight\":\"0\",\"imageorient\":\"0\",\"imagewidth\":\"0\",\"l10n_source\":\"0\",\"layout\":\"0\",\"linkToTop\":\"0\",\"list_type\":\"\",\"media\":\"0\",\"pages\":\"\",\"pi_f